import React from 'react'
import {Col, Row} from 'antd'
import {Text} from '../../../UIComponents/Typography/Text'
import {useTranslation} from 'react-i18next'
import {ArrowRightSvg} from '../../../Icons/Arrow'

export const AccountActionsBlock = ({recordsCount}) => {
    const {t} = useTranslation()
    
    return (
        <Row gutter={[0, 16]}>
            <Col span={24}>
                <Row wrap={false} justify='space-between'>
                    <Col>
                        <Text>{t('about_me')}</Text>
                        <Text>{t(('passport_number_birth_living_place'))}</Text>
                    </Col>
                    <Col>
                        <ArrowRightSvg/>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Col>
            <Col span={24}>
                <Row wrap={false} justify='space-between'>
                    <Col>
                        <Text>{t('records')}</Text>
                        <Text>{recordsCount}</Text>
                    </Col>
                    <Col>
                        <ArrowRightSvg/>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Col>
        </Row>
    )
}
